The handsome, Body-by-Fisher passenger car styling of a Chevrolet Sedan Delivery
makes an attractive advertisement for the business it serves. Ideal for lightweight
deliveries, this economical model is built to carry merchandise speedily and efficiently,
at lowest costs per mile. Single tone passenger car colors are available; 2-tone color
combinations on special order at additional cost.
